  “Michael Bublé is synonymous with Christmas, and what is more Christmassy than Jingle Bells?” – Jessica Steyn  Today’s Christmas song was chosen by Lowvelder’s News Editor, Mireille de Villiers.   Today’s Christmas song was chosen by Lowvelder’s News Editor, Mireille de Villiers.  She says that Laurika Rauch’s Somer Kersfees is special to her because it is proudly South African and the lyrics that were written by Koos du Plessis were so moving. This song is applicable to all South Africans regardless of their faith.